    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦为什么要为新的权力斗争做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/zimbabwe-protests-why-harare-is-bracing-for-a-new-power-struggle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的总统艾默森·曼南格瓦（Emmerson Mnangagwa）曾多次坚持他将在第二任期结束时退休。尽管如此，尽管如此，猜测仍在猜测，他可以寻求将自己的任期延长到这一宪法限制之外。如果他拒绝通过总统警棍，这为潜在的权力斗争奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/zimbabwe-protests-why-harare-is-bracing-for-a-new-power-struggle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国说查戈斯交易提供了控制，缓冲和外国部队禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uk-says-chagos-deal-provides-control-buffer-foreign-forces-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位英国部长说，英国与毛里求斯在查戈斯群岛的主权方面正在与毛里求斯进行促进，这将使欧洲国家完全控制印度洋和周围电磁频谱的重要联合军事基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uk-says-chagos-deal-provides-control-buffer-foreign-forces-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 12:41:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利总统波里克说，特朗普试图成为“皇帝”。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-attempting-to-be-an-emperor-chile-president-boric-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利的左派总统加布里埃尔·波里奇（Gabriel Boric）周三猛烈抨击唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump），他是一名假装皇帝，比美国国家元首预期宣布贸易关税的宣布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-attempting-to-be-an-emperor-chile-president-boric-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 12:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度议员辩论有争议的穆斯林财产法变更</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/indian-lawmakers-debate-controversial-muslim-property-law-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府正在敦促修改数十年来管理的法律，该法律是为了宗教和慈善目的而捐赠的穆斯林拥有的财产，这一举动可能会进一步侵蚀该国的少数派权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/indian-lawmakers-debate-controversial-muslim-property-law-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 11:53:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国人在勒笔获得生命线时承受压力的最大右</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/french-far-right-to-keep-up-pressure-as-le-pen-gets-lifeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的国家集会计划抗议它所谓的“法官暴政”，即使上诉法院在周二晚些时候在一份惊喜声明中表示，它应该能够在2026年中期对Marine Le Pen的挑战进行裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/french-far-right-to-keep-up-pressure-as-le-pen-gets-lifeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
